        <!-- TITLE -->
        <mxCell id="9" value="&lt;b&gt;Aura Promptly — Observability Stack (v1.1)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Two-layer architecture: CloudWatch (always-on) + Grafana Cloud (optional) + LiteLLM Spend Dashboard"
